### System overview
* BeagleBone Rev A6

### Setup environment
* For toolchain run on **Ubuntu 14.04 64bits**

  	  	$ sudo dpkg --add-architecture i386
  	  	$ sudo apt-get install gcc-multilib g++-multilib

* Extract toolchain under **tool/arm-2014.05-29-arm-none-linux-gnueabi-i686-pc-linux-gnu.tar.bz2**

### Build
* build all

        $ make dist

### Install
* SD card needs 2 partitions, **BOOT** and **ROOTFS**
* copy **dist/boot/\*** to **BOOT** partition
* copy **dist/userland/\*** **ROOTFS** partition

### note
* Check dependent shared library for an **OBJ**

        $ objdump -p OBJ | grep NEEDED

* Directory tree
    * **proj.mk**
    * **Makefile**
        * project scope Makefile
    * **prebuilt/**
        * prebuilt files, copy to final system image
    * **package/**
        * software packages
    * **tool/toolchain/**
        * Sourcery CodeBench Lite for Arm GNU/Linux Release
    * **dist/**
        * distributed files
